subject: Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: The freshman guard Brandon Triche scored a season-high 21 points, Andy Rautins added 18, and No. 10 Syracuse beat its upstate rival Cornell, 88-73, on Tuesday night at the Carrier Dome.
